text: Tsvetanka Stancheva (born 18 August 1929) is a Bulgarian gymnast. She competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Bulgarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
